features: 【9-in-1 Kitchen Knife Set】This universal kitchen knife set includes 7.7" Chef’s Knife, 6.7" Santoku Knife, 7.9" Bread Knife, 5.3" Utility Knife, 3.8" Paring Knife, Kitchen Scissors, Knife Sharpener, Vegetable Peeler and a stainless steel Knife Block.

【High Quality Knife Block Set】The professional knives set for kitchen is made of high carbon stainless steel, prevent rust and corrosion. The blade of each knife is carefully polished, and the V-shaped opening edge is sharper and maintains the cutting feel.

【Easy Storage & Clean】Rinse the knives under running water after use, then wipe it clean. When not in use, knives can be stored in the knife holder, keeping the countertop tidy, and not taking up too much space. Detachable base with drain hole is easy to clean and dry, prevents rust.

【Versatility】This knife set can meet all needs of your kitchen like chopping, slicing and dicing meat, vegetables, fruit and bread. Kitchen scissors also have the function of a bottle opener and clamping nuts, the peeler can peel the skin of fruits and vegetables, and the sharpener keeps the knife sharp at all times.

【Lifetime Service】 This premium knife set with block is still a ideal gift for friends and family who love cooking. We provide 18 months quality assurance and friendly customer service for our products. If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very Sharp Knives !
reviews.reviewText: It was honestly a great item, especially the knives. The silver metal container could be crafted or heavier because the quality of it does not match the quality of the knives. The knives are very sharp, so please be careful when using them. They are a nice-looking set with designs on the blade. They are dishwasher-friendly but avoid it if you want them to last and keep their quality. I love that it is small and compact storage for them, and you can add some more in the container as well because it's spacious.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewText: This is a great knife Set. I like that it comes with a sharpener. The knife holder looks nice on the countertop and it looks really expensive despite being so affordable. I haven't had it for long but it looks like it will last a long time.
